  "name": "Nagaraja COU1 — Non-cannulated pedicle screw compression-bending credibility assessment (Minimal Profile)",
  "description": "V&V 40 credibility assessment for FEA prediction of ASTM F1717 static compression-bending performance of a non-cannulated 7.5 mm pedicle screw construct. The FEA model ensemble (FDA, Ansys, DePuy Synthes) is compared against N=11 experimental constructs across two laboratories for the intended use of pre-market submission support under 21 CFR 888.3076. All 13 V&V 40 factors assessed; one factor (Test conditions) below required level due to single test condition. Intended use scope is described in the bound Requirement and Claim nodes; the structured context-of-use object is not separately linked under this minimal profile declaration.",
