      "rationale": "All three FEA codes (FDA in-house, Ansys, DePuy Synthes) are subject to documented software quality assurance programs including version control, regression testing, and release validation consistent with Gradation 2 requirements. No custom solver modifications were introduced for this analysis."
    },
    {
