      "factorStatus": "assessed",
      "acceptanceCriteria": "Achieved level must meet or exceed required level.",
      "rationale": "The validation activities replicate the ASTM F1717 test configuration that directly corresponds to the intended regulatory submission use. The experimental setup, loading conditions, and specimen geometry are representative of the non-cannulated 7.5 mm pedicle screw construct described in the bound Requirement and Claim, confirming Gradation 3 relevance of validation activities to the intended use scope."
    }
